name: Leech in Hands
description:
3 out of 3 Dream collage series
* ✧･ﾟ: ✧･Based on my own dream that night.･ﾟ✧:･ﾟ✧ *

In this dream I pinched my own arms, and took out leeches from both left and right easily without any pain. And then I said “So it was these things this whole time.. huff. Thank God It’s out”
